data.description: If small town country living is what you are searching for, as they say " the search is over"! Nestled between the small towns of Greenwood  and Ellendale, 13326 Owens Rd  offers that convenience and is a short 20 minute drive to Milton and all the Delaware beaches have to offer! This home has a brand new metal roof and scalloped siding graces the face of the home.  The first floor has a full Living room, Kitchen and Dining area with a sliding back door that overlooks the back yard. Laundry area, powder room and access to the attached garage are also located off the kitchen  on the first floor. The second floor features the Primary bedroom with a full bathroom and 2 additional bedrooms and additional full bathroom for the family or guests. Bedrooms have been freshly painted and are ready to move in! The exterior features a deck off the back sliding door with and awning and fish pond for relaxing and enjoying the upcoming fall season while enjoying the outdoor grilling area or any recreation you desire! Schedule this home at the top of your list today and picture yourself in a rocking chair on the front porch this weekend!
